Victoria (palʊla-ɩ Alexandria Victoria cejewiye taa, [[agoza fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 24 pɩnaɣ 1819 Kensington kewiyaɣ ɖɩɣa taa [[Lɔndrɩ|Londre]] tɛtʊ taa nɛ ɛsɩ [[kɔlaɣ fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 22 pɩnaɣ [[1901]] Osborne House (Isle of Wight). Ɛɛkɛ [[Kewiyaɣ Kɩkpɛndaɣ]] ñʊʊ tʊ pʊtɔbʊʊ se abiɖe Pretagne Sɔsɔʊ nɛ Irɩlandɩ ajɛyɛ taa [[Mɩsɩkʋm fenaɣ|mɩsɩkʊm fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 20 pɩnaɣ 1837 pɩkɔɔ pɩtalɩ ɖooo ɛ-sɩm alɩwaatʊ. Kpaɣnɛ pɩnaɣ 1867 [[hasɩyaɖɛ fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ kajalaɣ ŋgʊ wiye ɛɛkɛ [[Kanadaa]] ɛjaɖɛ taa abiɖe nɛ ɖɔɖɔ [[Ɛndɩ]] ɛjaɖɛ tɛ wiyaʊ sɔsɔ (abiɖe) kpaɣnɛ [[agoza fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 1 pɩnaɣ 1876 nɛ pʊwayi ɖɔɖɔ ɛtɛzɩna [[Ositraalii]] ɛjaɖɛ pɩnaɣ 1901 [[kɔlaɣ fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 1 ŋgʊ wiye. Ɛɛwɛna pɩnzɩ 18 lɛ, ɛkpaɣ kewiyaɣ kpelaɣ.
